  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The intervention will consist in a 6 week of pilates practice in older population to check
      the prevention of fall effectiveness.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A study population of elder people will be randomly allocated to intervention or control
      group, consisted in Pilates and a booklet of balance tips respectively.

      The protocol will be performed for 6 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
